{"tid":1351973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 喺現場揸大聲公傳播情報嘅朋友，請意識到自己有好大fact check責任","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T03:23:44.000Z","uid":274475,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"819b99797a903ccfe776a472155547732b4c2383","tid":1351973,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:20.000Z","msg":"發夢琴晚響港島，好多揸大聲公嘅朋友一直嗌好多<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">未經證實/冇意義/錯誤嘅資訊</span></strong>，例如:<br />\n<br />\n1. 前線已放催淚彈 (事實: 係手足出煙攻)<br />\n<br />\n2. 後方金鐘已經俾狗清哂 (事實: 金鐘根本一直冇正式set防線，何來俾狗清)<br />\n<br />\n3. 中環站有白衫黑社會出緊黎打人 (事實: 完全鳩講)<br />\n<br />\n4. IFC有狗落緊黎/ 金鐘有狗包抄緊 (事實: 完全鳩講again)<br />\n<br />\n明白大家響現場都會緊張，但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">揸住大聲公/跑住嗌資訊嘅你要意識到，你傳播嘅資訊係會影響在場戰友好多判斷。老實講，好多錯嘅資訊根本係製造恐慌，搞到好多本身仲可以留嘅戰友覺得好危險要退。</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢個問題已經存在左好多晚，最誇張係爆入立會果晚有一段時間煲底係咁有人嗌警總有速龍，我真係心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，先唔講警總咁撚遠，警總冇速龍先奇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e448561fd9608d590af1da6883574e44b640d03a","tid":1351973,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53c13959740867ea2efd164c47b8056c05821c18","tid":1351973,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:01:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b1d8078a74560a6ea4c6af49cd70a4ea25e45113","tid":1351973,"uid":12816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0bc2dae4b895a5a202cd0d2e4bac8d767e3628","tid":1351973,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"揸大聲公講資訊朋友請緊記:<br />\n<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 一定要fact check左先講</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2. 無意義零碎資訊唔洗講 (例如太遠地方有警車等)"},{"pid":"1651ce8678cfc74b7ea23583099d2fc41b5d6042","tid":1351973,"uid":274475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:08:58.000Z","msg":"同埋其實琴晚網絡完全暢通，響中後方根本唔特別需要人叫咪講資訊，大家自己睇TG就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫咪資訊係叫俾前線上哂gear睇唔到電話嘅手足聽，但叫俾前線聽真係要諗清楚<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真確+有用</span></strong>資訊先好講，否則前線根據錯誤資訊做錯判斷傷害力好大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(當然最前自己有對講機，但第二三排好多都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"3188b591392d381b1591f88edbdc97c2098b1a16","tid":1351973,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"428263e39257720ec8d429d28b7fabbc6f553edc","tid":1351973,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:25:12.000Z","msg":"好好審核下d資訊先講"},{"pid":"55db5d96d577e4249fc3699d5bd99d362e7bf856","tid":1351973,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:53:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"982e59dd578bc84d487b4b6e85b336e9213edce3","tid":1351973,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"推for weekend行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b37e7469a53b57a03ac5732391d4502188252e5","tid":1351973,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:22:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">727對準鄉黑：南邊圍福德堂</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i1.wp.com/tmhk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMAGE-2019-07-22-034503.jpg?fit=1280%2C852&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ftmhk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FIMAGE-2019-07-22-034503.jpg%3Ffit%3D1280%252C852%26ssl%3D1&h=144559cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180303/photo/bkn-20180303174105327-0303_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180303182522\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180303%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180303174105327-0303_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180303182522&h=b7b43767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.postimg.cc/d1RbdsTg/yl-1-2-gate.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fd1RbdsTg%2Fyl-1-2-gate.jpg&h=53120000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當日疑接載白衫鄉黑的車牌：<br />\n<br />\nVW 9089<br />\nWZ 7266<br />\nNT 21<br />\nVL 9886<br />\nTM 790"},{"pid":"4c70a529f255a7bd1f12601e1e29f3f6bdbab068","tid":1351973,"uid":235370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}